I have this audio file that claims: "Compared to regular audio, the subliminal affirmation messages are recorded at many different frequencies and volumes, therefore you will be unable to hear the messages consciously."

Using audacity:

https://www.audacityteam.org/

I took this 3 min clip:

https://drive.google.com/file/d/1QXrR45OfBKxGzG9ksBSNhrFKHE5cexSE/view

And tried changing the Pitch up and down but can't find the messages. Is there a technique for this?

Original youtube link: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GXeAOtb1VeA

Here is a list of all the subliminal affirmations/messages in this recording.

My happiness grows stronger every day

My energy levels are naturally very high

I choose to be happy and free

Life is good

I feel good

I am a great communicator

I am a confident person

I am a fun, friendly, and out-going person

I succeed in everything I do
